Instructions
access to cluster on aws:

Install awscli follow these steps please:
sudo yum install awscli -y
aws --version
python -m pip install awscli -y
sudo yum install python-pip -y
sudo pip install awscli

Upgrade the pip command:
sudo pip install --upgrade pip

Upgrade awscli:
aws --version
sudo pip install awscli --upgrade

aws sts get-caller-identity

Get access key and secret key:
--> go to iam to your username and click on it to get the access & secret key, then run the follow command:
aws configure
aws sts get-caller-identity
aws eks --region eu-west-1 update-kubeconfig --name acirrustech
kubectl get nodes




 
